metadata.name: aiLI8NS #4967 (Genesis)
metadata.description:
aiLI8NS have been spawned by the 8liens 

They are a series of ARTS Created & Created by Arwyn, on behalf of and for the PEP8LIEN community.

ZERO TRAIT Tokens with an emphasis on bringing Frogs and 8liens together.

This aiLI8N #4967 Represents his matching counterpart 8lien #4967 but after falling through a time-hole, lost his traits, but found his Mojo.

This inaugural 8lien was initially airdropped to all FROGTENDERS and will be continually spawned, to meet demand and raise funds for the PEP8LIEN Project.
